videos.headline: Johnson's leaping grab a catch-of-the-year candidate
videos.description: Trace McSorley tosses a 31-yard pass to Juwan Johnson, who leaps high and snags the ball with one hand.

videos.headline: McSorley motors downfield for 51 yards
videos.description: Trace McSorley keeps it himself, has a whole lot of open field as he goes 51 yards to the Ohio State 31-yard line.

videos.headline: Taylor catches deflected pass for interception
videos.description: Dwayne Haskins' pass deflects off his receiver and Garrett Taylor catches the interception and returns it 45 yards.

videos.headline: Hamler outruns defenders on 93-yard TD
videos.description: Trace McSorley tosses a pass to KJ Hamler, who speeds past multiple defenders all the way to the end zone for a 93-yard touchdown.

videos.headline: Haskins finds Dobbins for 26-yard TD
videos.description: Dwayne Haskins flips a pass to J.K. Dobbins, who goes 26 yards into the end zone for the touchdown.

videos.headline: Hamler's speed keeps Penn State ahead at halftime
videos.description: Penn States holds a 13-7 lead over Ohio State at halftime behind KJ Hamler's 93-yard touchdown in the second quarter.

tracking.trackingName: COM_NCF Highlight (Hamler's speed keeps Penn State ahead at halftime) 2018/09/29 ESHEET

videos.headline: Dobbins finds his way through for a TD
videos.description: Dwyane Haskins bobbles the snap, but gets it to J.K. Dobbins quickly, who weaves his way for a 4-yard touchdown run.

videos.headline: Penn State's Shelton ejected for targeting
videos.description: Ohio State's K.J. Hill gets hit in the head late by Penn State's Antonio Shelton, who is ejected for targeting after review.

videos.headline: Buckeyes' Young deflects pass to force turnover
videos.description: Ohio State's Chase Young deflects Trace McSorley's pass and it falls incomplete, causing Penn State to turn it over on downs.

videos.headline: Ohio State's Pryor ejected for targeting
videos.description: Trace McSorley connects with KJ Hamler for a 36-yard play, but gets hit in the head by Isaiah Pryor, who is ejected for targeting.

videos.headline: Freiermuth hauls in TD with one hand
videos.description: Trace McSorley lobs a high pass into the end zone to Pat Freiermuth, who secures the touchdown with one hand.

videos.headline: Haskins stopped on fourth down
videos.description: Dwayne Haskins keeps it himself to try and convert on fourth down, but Penn State's defense thwarts the attempt.

videos.headline: Sanders carries pile of defenders into end zone
videos.description: Miles Sanders takes the handoff and muscles into the end zone for a touchdown, extending Penn State's lead.

videos.headline: Victor sheds tackle, dodges another for TD
videos.description: Dwayne Haskins tosses a pass to Binkimen Victor, who sheds a tackle as he makes the catch and dodges another and goes 47 yards for the TD.

videos.headline: Hill breaks tackle on go-ahead TD
videos.description: Dwayne Haskins tosses a quick pass to K.J. Hill, who breaks a tackle and runs 24 yards for the score that puts Ohio State ahead.

videos.headline: Young's big stop gives Buckeyes the win
videos.description: Miles Sanders gets tackled for a loss on fourth down by Chase Young as the Buckeyes take over and hold on for a 27-26 win.

videos.headline: Meyer: 'One of the best wins I have ever been a part of'
videos.description: Urban Meyer explains how Ohio State was able to fight past Penn State for a 27-26 win on Saturday night.

videos.headline: Haskins says win is a 'momentum shifter'
videos.description: Dwayne Haskins reacts to Ohio State's win over Penn State and how it affects the team's momentum going forward this season.

videos.headline: Haskins leads Ohio State past Penn State
videos.description: Dwayne Haskins leads a game-winning 96-yard touchdown drive and Penn State fails to convert on fourth down sending Ohio State to a 27-26 win.

tracking.trackingName: COM_NCF Highlight (Haskins leads Ohio State past Penn State) 2018/09/29 ESHEET SOTFULL

videos.headline: Haskins silences Happy Valley and doubters
videos.description: Dwayne Haskins leads two clutch drives on the road in front of a crowd of 110,000-plus to boost Ohio State's playoff odds.

tracking.trackingName: COM_NCF Highlight (Haskins silences Happy Valley and doubters) 2018/09/29 ESHEET ENHL
